setwd("~/Documents/CURS 2017-2018/MLLG/Entregable 1")
options(contrasts = c("contr.sum", "contr.treatment"))
library(car)
library(lsmeans)
## Loading required package: estimability
ddt<-read.csv2("FS2.csv")
noms<-read.csv2("llista.csv")
ne<-30
ddt$Stres<-as.factor(ddt$Stres)
for (est in 1:ne){
  plot(c(0, 1), c(0, 1), ann = F, bty = 'n', type = 'n', xaxt = 'n', yaxt = 'n')
  text(x = 0.5, y = 0.5, paste(noms[est,2]), cex = 1.5, col = "black")
  write(paste(noms[est,2]),"")
  dd<-ddt[ddt$est==est,3:6]  
  m00<-lm(FS~1,dd)
  write("           Apartado 1)","")
  write("","")
  write("                  a)","")
  write("","")
  print(summary(m0<-lm(FS~Stres,dd)))
  plot(predict(m0),resid(m0))
  abline(h=0,lty=2)
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  write("                  b)","")
  write("","")
  print(anova(m00,m0))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  print(ao0<-anova(m0))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  print(lsm0<-lsmeans(m0,~Stres))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  write("                  c)","")
  write("","")
  print(cld(lsm0))
  write("===========================================================================","")
  write("","")
  write("           Apartado 2)","")
  write("","")
  write("                  a)","")
  write("","")
  print(summary(m<-lm(FS~Stres*RAD,dd)))
  plot(predict(m),resid(m))
  abline(h=0,lty=2)
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  write("                  b)","")
  write("","")
  print(aomm<-anova(m00,m))
  print(aomm1<-anova(m0,m))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  print(ao<-Anova(m,ty=3))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  print(lsmp<-lsmeans(m,~Stres,trend="RAD"))
  print(cld(lsmp))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  print(lsm<-lsmeans(m,~Stres|RAD))
  print(cld(lsm))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  print(lsm2<-lsmeans(m,~Stres|RAD,at=list(RAD=c(400,600))))
  print(cld(lsm2))
  write("===========================================================================","")
  write("","")
  write("           Apartado 3)","")
  write("","")
  write("                  a)","")
  write("","")
  print(summary(ma<-lm(FS~Stres+RAD,dd),ty=3))
  plot(predict(ma),resid(ma))
  abline(h=0,lty=2)
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  write("                  b)","")
  write("","")
  print(aomma<-anova(m00,ma))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  print(aoa<-Anova(ma,ty=3))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  print(lsma<-lsmeans(ma,~Stres))
  print(cld(lsma))
  write("===========================================================================","")
  write("","")
  write("           Apartado 4)","")
  write("","")
  write("                  Recta","")
  write("","")
  print(summary(mrt<-lm(RAD~T,dd),ty=3))
  write("------------------------------------------------","")
  write("","")
  write("                  Parbola","")
  write("","")
  print(summary(mrt2<-lm(RAD~T+I(T^2),dd),ty=3))
  print(anova(lm(RAD~1,dd),mrt2))
  print(anova(mrt,mrt2))
  print(vif(mrt2))
}
